        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>DOD Portfolio Management Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to submit a plan to identify, develop, and acquire databases, analytical and financial tools, and workforce skills to improve the assessment, management, and optimization of weapon system investments, including through consolidation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
